originalText.text: They lied to me, both the clerk at the front desk and Dr. Teter, who told me that they accepted my insurance and that the lab where my biopsy was sent to would be part of my insurance and that I “may” have to pay 10%” that’s all!”  Then they sent me a bill for 10% paid and I have to pay 90%!  Be very careful, they are scam artists!

Dr. Speilfogel is a GREAT Doctor.  His manner and way of handling patients is wonderful.
I have been to him for various foot problems and conditions and he handles my painful feet so well. I walk out smiling and know that my discomfort and pain -if not gone then -will be gone with his care soon.
Cannot say enough great things about him.

originalText.text: Dr. Spielfogel and the intern doctor who saw me were extremely courteous, professional, and helpful to address and solve the foot problem that I had.
